Fill the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/blender/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 blender}} with ice and add the Mango Margarita Mix, tequila, and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/triple-sec/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 triple sec}}. Blend until smooth. Rub the rim of a margarita glass with a lime wedge and dip into Mint Salt to coat rim. Fill glass and enjoy!\
